data.description: Rare 3 bedroom, 2 bath fully furnished condo at Seventh Mountain Resort with beautiful interior and stunning views of Deschutes National Forest. Open-concept kitchen is fully equipped, has sturdy wood cabinetry, and new dishwasher. The family room is the perfect place to get cozy by the fireplace, next to the private balcony with priceless views. Master queen bedroom has private full bath. 2nd queen bedroom has Jack and Jill bath. 3rd bedroom furnished with queen/twin bunk. Full use of resort amenities, including pools, hot tubs, sauna, fitness center, tennis and pickleball courts, mini golf, and playgrounds. Other activities include ice skating, white water rafting, skiing, and backyard access to some of the best hiking and mountain biking trails in the Pacific NW. Seventh Mountain is the closest resort to Mt. Bachelor Ski Resort and 7 miles from downtown Bend.
